# Forecast Engine

## Modules (app/server/services/forecast)

- ForecastEngine.ts — orchestrator
- DataLoaderService.ts — DB→cache hydration
- AccountRegisterService.ts — register operations in forecast context
- ReoccurrenceService.ts — scheduling logic and splits
- RegisterEntryService.ts — entry calculations and projection flags
- LoanCalculatorService.ts — interest and amortization calculations
- TransferService.ts — inter-account transfer validation and effects
- DataPersisterService.ts — cache→DB persistence for projections/snapshots
- DateTime.ts and DateTimeService.ts — date/time utilities and edge-case handling
- ModernCacheService.ts — fast in-memory storage
- getProjectedBalanceAtDate.ts — convenience function for at-date projections
- lib/rateLimiter.ts, logger.ts, types.ts — support utilities and typings

## Tests

- Unit and integration suites cover edge cases, regression scenarios, and performance baselines under app/server/services/forecast/__tests__
- Snapshot tests capture multi-month scenarios (e.g., threeMonthLoanAndReoccurrence)
- Use scripts in app/package.json to run subsets or the full suite

## Change guidance

- Modify services with clear separation of concerns; prefer pure functions when possible for predictability
- Extend types.ts and shared utilities rather than inlining ad‑hoc structures
- Update or add tests for new edge cases (month boundaries, DST changes, interval adjustments, transfer cycles)

